com.intel.fightclub.dialog

Class DialogueConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.DialogueConstants

  • @Immutable
public final class DialogueConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants in the DialogManager became a little bit too many, so having a separate utility class will help remove a little bit of clutter from it. Queries/actions, commentary and some other related constants for the DialogManager will be defined here.
